take a look?

06:01.361 --> 06:04.996
Yeah, I can... I can
take a quick look-see.

06:04.998 --> 06:06.498
(CHUCKLES)

06:06.500 --> 06:08.533
Chain. Chain.

06:09.102 --> 06:10.836
(CLANK)

06:11.704 --> 06:12.204
Ugh.

06:12.206 --> 06:14.840
Wait. Is this one
of those soviet bikes?

06:14.842 --> 06:17.609
'Cause I only deal
with American equipment.

06:17.611 --> 06:18.410
Huh?
USA!

06:18.412 --> 06:21.313
Maybe I'll just have
my dad fix it.
(CHUCKLES)

06:21.315 --> 06:23.548
Makes sense.
Keep it in the family.

06:24.350 --> 06:26.418
(CLANK)
(GROANS LOUDLY)

06:27.420 --> 06:29.254
Aah!
Are you okay?

06:29.256 --> 06:31.723
Mmm-hmm.
Are you crying?

06:31.725 --> 06:33.091
No. (EXHALES)

06:33.093 --> 06:35.394
Good talking.
(WHIMPERING)

06:36.596 --> 06:37.996
<i>My plan was a complete bust.</i>

06:37.998 --> 06:42.200
<i>I only had one option left...</i>
<i>Call in the big guns.</i>

06:42.202 --> 06:46.538
So what happened to "I'm 12.
I gotta go it alone"?

06:46.540 --> 06:47.506
That didn't work out
so great.

06:47.508 --> 06:53.545
Well, you're safe now.
Love's my business,
and business is booming.

06:53.547 --> 06:55.313
So what do we got?

06:55.715 --> 06:57.282
Okay. Her name's Dana.

06:57.284 --> 07:00.218
She's 13,
lives down the block.

07:00.220 --> 07:01.887
She smells like
fruity pebbles.

07:01.889 --> 07:03.555
Pfft.

07:03.557 --> 07:04.823
Why are you
asking Pops for help

07:04.825 --> 07:07.192
when you got
all the resources
you need right here?

07:07.194 --> 07:08.460
You don't know anything
about girls.

07:08.462 --> 07:11.930
I know a ton. I've got
a super hot girlfriend.

07:11.932 --> 07:14.166
Yeah, from Canada
that no one's ever seen.

07:14.168 --> 07:16.902
'Cause I met her at camp,
ya sausage gobbler.

07:16.904 --> 07:20.038
You couldn't come up
with something
a little more original?

07:20.040 --> 07:22.941
I mean, a fake girlfriend...
In Canada?

07:22.943 --> 07:26.178
Hey! There's nothing fake
about her except her boobs!

07:26.180 --> 07:30.782
Yep, they're huge and real...
But they're also fake.

07:30.784 --> 07:33.084
You know what?
I don't have to
explain it to you.

07:33.086 --> 07:34.820
I'm outta here.

07:36.088 --> 07:38.924
Her breasts sound
very complicated.

07:38.926 --> 07:41.326
So where are we at
with this Dana girl?

07:41.328 --> 07:44.596
Well, I've been secretly
following her around
for two weeks.

07:44.598 --> 07:46.331
Creating a sense
of mystery.

07:46.333 --> 07:47.933
And today I broke
her bicycle.

07:47.935 --> 07:51.503
Good. You made a memorable
first impression.

07:51.505 --> 07:52.771
And I kinda cried
in front of her.

07:52.773 --> 07:55.440
Some women like
a sensitive man.

07:55.442 --> 07:58.376
You think?
You can't help him, Pops.

07:58.378 --> 07:59.644
He's un-help-able.

07:59.646 --> 08:02.214
He'll never get a girlfriend
even half as hot as mine.

08:02.216 --> 08:05.383
Oh, yeah? What's her name?
Tell me right now. Go.

08:05.385 --> 08:06.952
Marion Lemieux.

08:06.954 --> 08:07.819
Marion Lemieux?

08:07.821 --> 08:09.688
Like Mario Lemieux,
the hockey player?

08:09.690 --> 08:12.724
Yeah! It's a common last name
in Canada,

08:12.726 --> 08:13.625
like "Smith" or "Jones."

08:13.627 --> 08:16.795
