be nice to you,
but forget it.

08:16.797 --> 08:18.864
I'm outta here.

08:19.866 --> 08:20.365
Okay.

08:20.367 --> 08:22.901
Your next move with Dana
is important.

08:22.903 --> 08:24.236
You gotta go for it.

08:24.238 --> 08:25.504
Make a big gesture...

08:25.506 --> 08:29.441
Something that'll show her
exactly how you feel.

08:29.443 --> 08:31.977
Pfft. Waste of time.

08:31.979 --> 08:32.577
Here we go.

08:32.579 --> 08:34.880
This nerd has no clue
with the ladies.

08:34.882 --> 08:36.715
Yeah? Let's call Marion
right now.

08:36.717 --> 08:38.783
Think I won't?
'Cause I will.

08:38.785 --> 08:40.318
That's what
I'm asking you to do.

08:40.320 --> 08:43.288
