I'm outta here.

08:57.937 --> 09:00.438
<i>Meanwhile, my Mom</i>
<i>and Erica were using</i>

09:00.440 --> 09:01.706
<i>the most cutting edge</i>
<i>technology</i>

09:01.708 --> 09:03.642
<i>to track down</i>
<i>a photo of Anita.</i>

09:03.644 --> 09:07.579
Mom.
<i>It was called microfiche.</i>

09:08.014 --> 09:09.347
Move.

09:09.349 --> 09:10.849
(GASPS) Oh, my God.

09:10.851 --> 09:14.719
It's amazing.
It only took us
two hours to find it.

09:14.721 --> 09:16.388
Hey, not bad, Dad.

09:16.390 --> 09:17.822
Okay, Erica, you saw her.

09:17.824 --> 09:20.425
