with your life.

09:21.260 --> 09:22.327
Hmm.

09:22.329 --> 09:24.162
Wait a minute.

09:24.664 --> 09:25.730
How do you...

09:25.732 --> 09:26.865
(RATTLING)
What?

09:26.867 --> 09:28.667
Make it bigger?
Well, okay, just...

09:28.669 --> 09:29.801
Make the picture bigger.
Okay, here.

09:29.803 --> 09:32.704
Where's the knob to make it
a bigger picture? It's just...
(PEOPLE SHUSHING)

09:32.706 --> 09:35.240
Mom, God!
That's as big as it goes.
Okay, okay.

09:35.242 --> 09:37.409
What is it?
Shh!

09:40.212 --> 09:40.679
Oh, no.

09:40.681 --> 09:45.016
<i>As always,</i>
<i>my mom took the bad news</i>
<i>with grace and dignity.</i>

09:45.018 --> 09:47.986
(BLEEPS) My ring.
Shh!

09:52.625 --> 09:54.125
Bevy!

09:55.227 --> 09:58.096
What a day! What a day!

09:58.098 --> 09:59.130
