10:00.567 --> 10:02.667
Your man is on fire.

10:02.669 --> 10:07.639
<i>By sheer chance,</i>
<i>my dad was in a rare</i>
<i>good mood that night.</i>

10:07.641 --> 10:09.874
<i>Unfortunately,</i>
<i>my mom was not.</i>

10:09.876 --> 10:11.242
What's happening?

10:11.244 --> 10:12.877
Nothing.

10:14.680 --> 10:15.213
Take a load off.

10:15.215 --> 10:18.850
Well, I usually
take a load off right there.

10:18.918 --> 10:21.453
