right here.

10:22.388 --> 10:23.455
What do you...

10:23.457 --> 10:26.825
Is there anything you wanna
tell me about this ring?

10:27.627 --> 10:29.461
It's a symbol of our love?

10:29.463 --> 10:31.529
Yes, that's very true.

10:31.531 --> 10:33.798
But, uh, tell me about that.

10:33.800 --> 10:38.436
What made you pick
this exact ring for me?

10:38.904 --> 10:42.073
When I saw it,
it spoke to me.

10:42.075 --> 10:44.175
Aw. What did it say?

10:44.177 --> 10:48.113
"I'm a pretty ring.
Buy me."

10:48.814 --> 10:50.148
"Buy me" for who?

10:50.150 --> 10:51.416
Oh, boy. (SIGHS)

10:51.418 --> 10:53.018
How could you give me
her ring?

10:53.020 --> 10:55.220
What do you think
I'm made of, diamonds?

10:55.222 --> 10:57.956
I... (HUFFS)
You can't just return these!

10:57.958 --> 11:02.260
Okay, well,
I have no problem
returning this one.

11:02.262 --> 11:03.862
Wait. Bevy!

11:03.864 --> 11:06.464
Let's talk about this.
Listen.

11:06.466 --> 11:08.867
If it'll make you feel
any better,

11:08.869 --> 11:11.369
I will get you a new ring.

11:11.371 --> 11:13.972
Great. Get me a new ring.

11:13.974 --> 11:15.740
What? You can't say that.

11:15.742 --> 11:17.442
Why would I get you
a new ring?

11:17.444 --> 11:18.376
It was your idea!

11:18.378 --> 11:20.645
Yeah, but I'm filled
with terrible ideas!

11:20.647 --> 11:23.415
