for God sake.

11:23.417 --> 11:26.151
Wow, Murray,
you are so romantic!

11:26.153 --> 11:28.620
Fine! I'll get you
a new ring!

11:28.622 --> 11:29.521
Fine!

11:29.523 --> 11:31.256
Fine!
Fine!

11:31.258 --> 11:31.823
Fine!

11:31.825 --> 11:34.192
<i>While my parents were calmly</i>
<i>working out their problems,</i>

11:34.194 --> 11:38.596
<i>I'd finally come up</i>
<i>with a solution</i>
<i>to my problems with Dana.</i>

11:38.598 --> 11:40.231
<i>(IN YOUR EYES</i> PLAYING)
(EXHALES)

11:40.233 --> 11:41.199
Let's do this,
Lloyd. (KISSES)

11:41.201 --> 11:45.203
<i>I'd use my favorite romantic</i>
<i>movie,</i> Say Anything,

11:45.205 --> 11:47.138
<i>to win Dana's heart.</i>

11:49.642 --> 11:52.711
<i>(IN YOUR EYES</i> PLAYING
ON BOOMBOX)

11:55.781 --> 11:57.849
<i>♪ Love</i>

12:00.586 --> 12:03.054
<i>♪ I get so lost</i>

12:03.155 --> 12:04.189
